OL,3,CGuernsey politician calls for
OL,4,Coutsourcing of tax and revenue services
OL,6,FA Guernsey politician wants the tax
OL,7,Frevenue service to be outsourced,
OL,8,Fafter important notices on how much
OL,9,Fincome tax people must pay were
OL,10,Fmistaken as scam emails.
OL,12,FDeputy Mark Helyar is arguing that
OL,13,FRevenue Services is "chronically
OL,14,Funderperforming", adding the States of
OL,15,FGuernsey is reluctant to "not only
OL,16,Freview the service it provides but
OL,17,Falso to outsource it".
