OL,3,CGuernsey politician calls for
OL,4,Coutsourcing of tax and revenue services
OL,6,FHe adds: "There are outsourcing
OL,7,Fentities that could be providing these
OL,8,Fservices much more cheaply and more
OL,9,Frapidly and efficiently."
OL,11,FHis comments come after annual coding
OL,12,Fnotices for 2025 were issued by email
OL,13,Ffor the first time over the weekend.
OL,15,FHowever, some islanders mistook the
OL,16,Femail from Revenue Services as a scam
OL,17,Fdue to its unexpected delivery.
