OL,4,Coutsourcing of tax and revenue services
OL,6,FThis important document - which
OL,7,Fdictates to employers how much income
OL,8,Ftax an individual must pay - was
OL,9,Fdeleted by many.
OL,11,FIn other cases, the email was
OL,12,Ferroneously directed to spam folders.
OL,14,FScam experts have suggested the email
OL,15,Fwas exactly the type that should be
OL,16,Fdeleted.
