OL,3,CGuernsey politician calls for
OL,4,Coutsourcing of tax and revenue services
OL,6,FInformation Security Consultant Nick
OL,7,FRobilliard says: "If you're going to
OL,8,Fchange your communication techniques,
OL,9,Fthen taking time to set that up
OL,10,Ftechnically with your IT team to make
OL,11,Fsure that your emails are not going to
OL,12,Fbe rejected by email filters is a good
OL,13,Fidea."
OL,15,FDeputy Helyar also voiced concerns
OL,16,Fabout the backlog of tax returns
OL,17,Fdating back to 2020 that Revenue
OL,18,FServices is currently dealing with.
